Package: scholr
Title: Scholarly Writing Utilities for R Markdown and LaTeX
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R:
    person("Omar", "Wasow", , "owasow@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Omar Wasow [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Omar Wasow <owasow@gmail.com>
Description: A collection of helper functions for creating publication-ready
    tables in R Markdown documents. Provides wrappers for stargazer, kable, and
    xtable with sensible defaults, automatic output format detection (LaTeX/HTML/text),
    and customizable variable label conversion for regression tables.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports:
    dplyr,
    stringr,
    knitr,
    kableExtra,
    stargazer,
    xtable,
    broom,
    scales,
    glue,
    lme4,
    purrr
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    rmarkdown,
    rstudioapi,
    pscl
Config/testthat/edition: 3
